ISLAMABAD, Sep 02 (APP): Federal Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb said on Friday that Prime Minister Shahbaz Sharif would visit Gilgit-Baltistan today (Friday) to assess the damage caused by the floods and monitor the ongoing rescue and relief operations.
In a tweet, she said a detailed briefing would be given to the PM regarding rains and floods in Gilgit-Baltistan.
